data.description: Welcome home to sophistication and tranquility! Discover contemporary luxury in this 4-bed, 3-bath country haven. Located in gorgeous Walton County and just moments from charming, downtown Monroe, it boasts a beautiful 2.25-acre lot that includes an enormous, fully insulated, second garage with private road access! Inside, you will find an open floor plan flooded with natural light and upscale finishes, such as granite countertops, a stone fireplace and stainless-steel appliances. The large master-on-main bathroom offers a lavish soaking tub, separate shower and double vanity, leading to a spacious walk-in closet.  Two additional bedrooms and a laundry room occupy the main floor of this country home, whereas upstairs you will find a completed bed/bonus room with full bath. A large, unfinished basement offers endless possibilities, with external access the expansive yard. Come see this gem for yourself!
